						"description": "Request password reset link (LOCAL users only).\n\n**Security Features:**\n- Email enumeration prevention (always returns same response)\n- Only works for LOCAL users\n- Token expires in 1 hour\n- Old tokens are invalidated\n\n**Development:**\n- Check application logs for reset token\n- Token format: UUID\n\n**Production:**\n- Reset link sent via email"
					},
